videos.headline: Buffalo QB rips a 42-yard TD pass
videos.description: Bulls quarterback Tyree Jackson unloads a 42-yard touchdown throw to wide receiver Anthony Johnson.

videos.headline: Bulls RB breaks loose for 42-yard TD
videos.description: Buffalo running back Jaret Patterson swivels through defenders and speeds to the end zone for a 42-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Bulls QB continues to let it fly, sets up rush TD
videos.description: Buffalo quarterback Tyree Jackson airs out a 59-yard completion to Anthony Johnson, setting up a 1-yard rushing touchdown for Kevin Marks.

videos.headline: Buffalo QB whips 3rd TD pass of 1st half
videos.description: Bulls quarterback Tyree Jackson continues his first-half onslaught with a 9-yard touchdown bullet to tight end Tyler Mabry.

videos.headline: Rutgers RB opens 4th quarter with TD
videos.description: Rutgers running back Raheem Blackshear cuts to the edge and gallops into the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown.
